                        Patients who have undergone significant weight loss or had children may require a breast lift or
                        mastopexy to achieve their desired result.
                        Breast augmentation is often performed as part of a Mommy Makeover, which can include
                        liposuction, tummy tuck (abdominoplasty), vaginal rejuvenation (labiaplasty or vaginoplasty),
